  "title": "Slider widget, remove refinements when at min and max",
  "body": "I thought there was an issue already opened for this but I am not able to find it.\n\nThe slider should remove the refinements when the min and max of the slider are equals to min and max of the dataset.\n\nFor wordpress, in instant search page we could have article, page, products. Product is the only one with price so if you refine with the price slider you won't be able to have article and page\n",
